<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Landing Page</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        ::selection {
            color: #ff6a00;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-image: url('food3new.jpg'); /* Replace with your image URL */
            background-size: cover;
            /* background-position: center; */
            color: white;
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            padding: 15px;
        }
        .navbar .heading {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
        .navbar .links {
            display: flex;
        }
        .navbar .links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 50px;
        }
        .navbar .links a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .content {
            position: absolute;
            top: 45%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 80%;
        }
        .animated-text {
            font-size: 4em;
            font-weight: bold;
            animation: color-change 2s linear infinite;
            justify-content: center;
            display: flex;
        }
        @keyframes color-change {
            0% {
                color: rgb(115, 4, 4);
            }
            50% {
                color: rgb(31, 79, 11);
            }
            100% {
                color: rgb(24, 3, 3);
            }
        }
        .description {
            margin-top: 55px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 3s ease-in forwards;
            color: rgb(70, 64, 64);
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
            } 
        }
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .animated-text {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            .description {
                font-size: 1em;
            }
            .navbar .heading {
                font-size: 1.8em;
            }
            .navbar .links a {
                font-size: 1.1em;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                width: 100%;
            }
            .animated-text {
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }
            .description {
                font-size: 0.9em;
            }
            .navbar .heading {
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }
            .navbar .links a {
                font-size: 1em;
                margin: 5px;
            }
            body{
                background-image: url(/food3new.jpg);
                background-position: center;
                background-repeat: no-repeat;
                background-size: cover;
            }
            .content {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .navbar {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                width: 100%;
            }
            .animated-text {
                font-size: 1.2em;
            }
            .description {
                font-size: 0.8em;
            }
            .navbar .heading {
                font-size: 1.2em;
            }
            .navbar .links a {
                font-size: 0.8em;
                margin: 5px;
            }
            body{
                background-image: url(/food3new.jpg);
                background-position: center;
                background-size: cover;
            }
            .content {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="heading">A Bite Of Happiness</div>
        <div class="links">
            <a href="/auth/signup" class="btn">Sign Up</a>
            <a href="/about " class="btn">About Us</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn">Contact Us</a>
            <a href="/auth/login" class="btn">Login</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="animated-text"><strong>"Good Food, Great Mood!"</strong></div>
        <div class="description">
            <p>Our Mess Management System makes dining easy and efficient Enjoy smooth <br>operations and  happier meals every day!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>


